### Create Deal
POST http://localhost:5041/api/Deals
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_JWT_TOKEN>

{
  "title": "Lunch Special",
  "description": "Discounted meal",
  "originalPrice": 10.00,
  "discountedPrice": 5.99,
